7.4. Credit costs
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Pursuant to the Danish Credit Agreements Act, &BANKNAVN. must calculate
the total sum to be paid for the various forms of utilisation of the
card account as the sum of the total loan amount and the total costs
related to the credit agreement, and to settle the annual costs on
percentage basis.
